{"tid":1058151,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【藝文合作】小弟用9891個兩毫砌維港","createTime":"2019-03-12T10:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T05:59:39.000Z","uid":143257,"like":2280,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"69e7c791e13959402bba02c7d503b2ca4d85fee1","tid":1058151,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aK5R4Bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaK5R4Bf.png&h=4815799f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y54vBrJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy54vBrJ.gif&h=9ffc5089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩隻小鳥飛入香港，棲於樹上。<br />\n<br />\n有一鳥遙指遠方曰：「前有一畫。」<br />\n<br />\n其畫無以名之名曰：香港<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉於畫側笑曰：「吾觀此畫，料作畫者必為嘲諷香港名不副實，非香港，乃臭港。」<br />\n<br />\n鸞鳥問：「何也？」<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉「畫中空空如也，盡由一枚枚銅板雕砌而成，乃譏誚香港眼目所及，唯錢至上，滿城盡是一陣銅臭味。」<br />\n<br />\n鸞鳥曰：「弗也，畫中有物，正看乃金光閃耀之維港。」<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉步正，畫中果有景物，其又笑曰：「子之愚甚也。雖有物，但作畫者用以譏誚香港正步入暗淡，君不見其維港正銹蝕腐朽，此城只重小利，顧享樂，陷紙醉金迷之幻象而不能脫。」<br />\n<br />\n鸞鳥曰：「吾雖見有銹霉銅錢，腐蝕溷濁，污穢暗啞。但若無日，便無夜；若無明，便無暗，此乃對比之理。所以若無銹錢，怎更顯清錢之亮貴？幸畫中仍不乏清錢，其亮如明月，其潔如寶璐，混濁中仍固守自我，散發微光，此乃維港之所以仍為維港也。力勸眾萬萬清錢堅持。物雖會蝕，但銹與濁之對比方能看清此城之本相也，所謂有危便有機，此才為作畫者本意。」<br />\n<br />\n二鳥爭持不下，只因正看成港側成空，遠近高低各不同。不識廬山真面目，觀點角度是緣中。<br />\n<br />\n是空無一物，還是畫中有物；是銹澀溷濁，還是更顯真象，任由觀畫者決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTN5qjs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTN5qjs.gif&h=937b4d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次嘅畫中故事嘅手筆，係揾左另一位巴打合作 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n# 西樓月如鈎 thanks<br />\n<br />\n最後如果大家中意同想睇多d 不如follow 我art.ig 同facebook page<br />\n當支持下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nig : gllh_art <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=ad1a2fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a><br />\nfb page : Giraffe leung lok hei  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgiraffellh%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=3c69198a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh/</a><br />\n<br />\n西樓月如鈎巴打：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/coooooolicecream/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcoooooolicecream%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=e571c627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/coooooolicecream/</a><br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/west_wingm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwest_wingm%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=bd9f3057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/west_wingm/</a>"},{"pid":"83810a8ac616c3f997fd932d369fb014cb0699ef","tid":1058151,"uid":54871,"like":2,"dislike":149,"score":-147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71eba2986e59a3ec5c199433dc4f0915cf755f95","tid":1058151,"uid":143257,"like":297,"dislike":5,"score":292,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fDAi4F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fDAi4F.gif&h=0284b449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KUsamf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KUsamf.png&h=ac7d7123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次呢幅作品全部都係正常金色兩毫，而係分左新淨（閃）同舊（啞），而新淨個啲噴左保護劑，令佢更閃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今次作品唔打算噴藥水令部分兩毫變黑，而係keep住呢種金金狀態，反光嘅時候會見到 ，唔反光嘅時候純粹見到一塊金板。<br />\n<br />\n而一段長時間後，冇噴保護劑兩毫會生銹，到時就會係生銹既背景中見到閃耀的維港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbb7a7db6c6870fd09db7018e8a0682e0ab7548","tid":1058151,"uid":7519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c82f115d95920304b13def4f2c2815f3c0e50d","tid":1058151,"uid":80787,"like":15,"dislike":96,"score":-81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"試下放個5蚊雞喺左上角做太陽"},{"pid":"7b6fa0f968d6748b1cc2ce47b997e7767c234775","tid":1058151,"uid":14739,"like":16,"dislike":60,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"砌完未？<br />\n點解睇唔出"},{"pid":"0c59e287b2566085fb0df34bdbd0d124032e546d","tid":1058151,"uid":80787,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"99c82f115d95920304b13def4f2c2815f3c0e50d","tid":1058151,"uid":80787,"like":15,"dislike":96,"score":-81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"試下放個5蚊雞喺左上角做太陽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"再劃個哈哈笑上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbeb46273fb1549d0b64d02e3bd46afd7da5538","tid":1058151,"uid":105908,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb74adf744623f4989b5fd9969e220e52e6bbe05","tid":1058151,"uid":64232,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"幅畫好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583003301cf4c8722ed2881f56a00c5c59725e79","tid":1058151,"uid":220799,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p